                     <interp inst="t17990220-45-person395" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I have known him twelve years, he is an upright just character as any man I ever knew.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17990220-45-person396">
                  BENJAMIN
                   COOPER
