                     <interp inst="t17990220-45-person396" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990220-45-person396" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am an architect and surveyor: I have known the prisoner fifteen years, he bears as good a character as ever I met with; he is a man I have been particularly intimate with, for a great while, I have done business with him, and conceive him to be as a worthy a man as any in this Court.</p>
